{"tid":1474245,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府想剝奪未來學生既思考能力","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T06:39:42.000Z","uid":103939,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c401378e1cb196260a64e5e4b3f85b7bc629b63","tid":1474245,"uid":103939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:02:22.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到出面有個post講緊林鄭想刪除中文卷3同4 但每個人都將個焦點擺左落廣東話度<br />\n我想講 係現有既制度下 新移民可以揀普通話考試 所以對廣東話既影響未必有太大影響<br />\n<br />\n我認為佢主要目的唔係收廣東話皮<br />\n係同建制派想將通識科變做選修科既目的一樣<br />\n說話聆聽係同批判性思考 理解能力息息相關 政府係想令學生失去思考能力 就會同啲藍絲同化 政府同中共係未來既政策就唔會受到質疑 唔會再有反抗政府既運動<br />\n<br />\n所以絕對唔可以俾呢條改革通過！！"},{"pid":"96cf1107bb10b69e85d2524e5040454cc879025c","tid":1474245,"uid":103939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"35a2b8b0645bb5b08191e9a652fb2fb9fa2de448","tid":1474245,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac357743